  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Better educational opportunities for Venezuelan migrants and refugees in Peru</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project seeks to improved and strengthened conditions for out-of-school migrant, refugee and host community children and adolescents, especially girls, to access formal and non-formal education. In order to achieve this result, the project will strengthen the capacities of authorities and public officials of national/subnational governments to manage the coverage of educational services. The access to information about the situation of out-of-school migrant and refugee children and adolescents will be also improved. Out-of-school children and adolescents will be identified, registered and participating in the non-formal education program.</narrative>
  </description>
